d and expect more classes to come!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight creatively!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605520/extras/513cff08430cf8a6bc52cd42ccf414b0.poster.avif?t=1708710354\" width=480 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605520/extras/513cff08430cf8a6bc52cd42ccf414b0.webm?t=1708710354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605520/extras/513cff08430cf8a6bc52cd42ccf414b0.mp4?t=1708710354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover new strategies! Combine your characters in interesting ways and get that bounty!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lots of items!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605520/extras/6f682ea0b7418e7b36a74264e4973e9f.poster.avif?t=1708710354\" width=480 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605520/extras/6f682ea0b7418e7b36a74264e4973e9f.webm?t=1708710354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605520/extras/6f682ea0b7418e7b36a74264e4973e9f.mp4?t=1708710354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Loot, buy and gear up. Lots of items to spice things up.",
